This file contains description of the various patterns that I used when
programming the application. It serves as a guideline for me and for anyone
who would want to contribute to the project.

1) Signals

Usage: Calling a method like a function (without knowledge about the object)
Files: common/signals.h

2) Properties

Usage: Being able to react on changes to a variable
Files: common/property.h common/propertyobserver.h

